languages.text: "Спугнем, Ваша Светлость. К тому моменту как блюстители закончат обыски, все крысы эти разбегутся и следы заметут"
"We'll spook them, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. By the time the enforcers finish their search, all the rats will have scattered and covered their tracks."

languages.text: 「怯えさせましょう、陛下。エンフォーサーが捜索を終える頃には、すべてのネズミが散り散りになって足跡を消しているでしょう。」
languages.original_text: "We'll spook them, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. By the time the enforcers finish their search, all the rats will have scattered and covered their tracks."

traits.locale_text: 「怯えさせましょう、陛下。エンフォーサーが捜索を終える頃には、すべてのネズミが散り散りになって足跡を消しているでしょう。」

languages.text: “我们会把他们吓跑的，大人。要是等执法者搜查完，那群老鼠恐怕早就跑没影了，就连脚印都会擦得干干净净。”
languages.original_text: "We'll spook them, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. By the time the enforcers finish their search, all the rats will have scattered and covered their tracks."

traits.locale_text: “我们会把他们吓跑的，大人。要是等执法者搜查完，那群老鼠恐怕早就跑没影了，就连脚印都会擦得干干净净。”

languages.text: "Wir werden sie erschrecken, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}! Wenn die Enforcer mit ihrer Suche fertig sind, sind sämtliche Ratten verschwunden und haben ihre Spuren verwischt."
languages.original_text: "We'll spook them, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. By the time the enforcers finish their search, all the rats will have scattered and covered their tracks."

traits.locale_text: "Wir werden sie erschrecken, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}! Wenn die Enforcer mit ihrer Suche fertig sind, sind sämtliche Ratten verschwunden und haben ihre Spuren verwischt."

languages.text: « On risque de leur faire peur, Votre Seigneurie. D'ici à ce que les prévôts finissent leur fouille, tous les rats auront quitté le navire… en prenant bien soin de couvrir leurs traces. »
languages.original_text: "We'll spook them, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. By the time the enforcers finish their search, all the rats will have scattered and covered their tracks."
